Search/Xapian version 1.0.3.0
=============================

This is Search::Xapian, a Perl XS frontend to the Xapian C++ search 
library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Makefile.PL looks for xapian-config on your PATH.  You can specify a path for
xapian-config by setting the XAPIAN_CONFIG environmental variable, and you
can specify a C++ compiler by setting the CXX environmental variable.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  The Xapian C++ search library, which can be downloaded by following
  the instructions on http://www.xapian.org/

